    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PlanetSprite is an online MMO where you create your own character, customize, interact, trade and play with other fellow players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please NOTE that the game is not fully released and there are so many content that are being released part by part.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the world of PlanetSprite here are some of the features that are already available in early access:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/1c027ef1d541ea662d874cc8c7872b0a.avif?t=1735960383\" width=376 height=66 /></span>-Player customization with your own inventory and equipment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/427b8e39e846f5c38d4e4ffac7461b63.poster.avif?t=1735960383\" width=532 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/427b8e39e846f5c38d4e4ffac7461b63.webm?t=1735960383\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/427b8e39e846f5c38d4e4ffac7461b63.mp4?t=1735960383\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/3c552c00ff8a20287d5e76f00ce815db.webp?t=1735960383\" width=360 height=63 /></span>-Player owned house</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/a6d0c91f0a05a5620265b82a0ff56d9f.poster.avif?t=1735960383\" width=744 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/a6d0c91f0a05a5620265b82a0ff56d9f.webm?t=1735960383\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/a6d0c91f0a05a5620265b82a0ff56d9f.mp4?t=1735960383\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/047552992e866f7b223e4a01cd027e6b.webp?t=1735960383\" width=427 height=61 /></span>-Chat and interact with players, objects, and non-player characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/23b5cd43cfde6212d97d7ca221c989d6.poster.avif?t=1735960383\" width=800 height=291 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/23b5cd43cfde6212d97d7ca221c989d6.webm?t=1735960383\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/fb01439c72123737dfb95d0ff541116d.webp?t=1735960383\" width=247 height=63 /></span>-Minigames</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/0d3b63759e9d3875d64f84cc27ae0a7f.poster.avif?t=1735960383\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319240/extras/0d3b63759e9d3875d64f84cc27ae0a7f.webm?t=1735960383\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co